# FinBiz Operator Console — example environment file
#
# These are PLACEHOLDERS, no real secrets. DO NOT commit a real .env — it's gitignored.
#
# The static site needs NO build-time secrets to build or run. There is no automated
# sync pipeline: the site is kept current by a Claude session that reads the Master Doc,
# regenerates src/content/*.ts, builds, and deploys to Netlify by hand. See
# docs/CONTENT-SYNC.md for that workflow. The values below are just handy pointers the
# session (or you) refer to.

# --- Netlify ----------------------------------------------------------------
# The live site the sync session deploys to. The site is NOT linked to the GitHub repo,
# so deploys are an explicit upload (Netlify CLI or MCP) at the end of a sync — see
# docs/DEPLOYMENT.md. No secret to store here; the site id is just a reference.
NETLIFY_SITE_ID=14bd8a31-376a-4941-a3f4-06e8c89015db

# --- Source-of-truth Google Doc ID (the long id from the Doc's URL) ----------
# The single FinBiz Master Doc — the source of truth. The repo only ever points to it;
# it is never copied in. Not a secret, but handy to keep here.
GOOGLE_DOC_ID_MASTER=1D93j3Pjo6HPqdtb6IiAPvb5DIp_cuZl4bU-bsBawexg
